         <title class="- topic/title ">General</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Bump cap/hard hat, safety glasses with foam liner, proper hearing protection,
            fire-resistant long sleeved shirt, safety toe boots. </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">
